ark><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(248, 243, 243); color: inherit\">She lost her husband, Gohan, and her father. She was one of the first to see how the virus worked, witnessing the slow deaths of the men around her. Along with 18, she formed a rescue team to protect other sur","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"A7WaRZ_lXRSK4K7T5vgkD.webp","creator":"SekiTheMC","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📺 Anime","👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👨 MalePov"],"chats":9199,"messages":121278,"created_at":"2025-07-10T03:47:56.085695+00:00"}